setCustomFilterProperties

public static void setCustomFilterProperties(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> properties)
Set custom filter properties. You can pass in custom properties like "age", "23" and add a filter "age > 20" on the vessel dashboard. Custom properties are not saved to the DB and need to be initialized on app startup.

Parameters:
properties - -Map of properties. Properties will be co-erced to required types. For boolean properties, expected values are "true" or "false"
